1
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:04,129
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

2
00:00:11,179 --> 00:00:13,019
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Rishia,
be honest.</b></Default>

3
00:00:13,179 --> 00:00:16,099
<Default><b>I need to know if you're
the one who broke my bracelet.</b></Default>

4
00:00:16,519 --> 00:00:18,190
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

5
00:00:18,649 --> 00:00:21,369
<Default><b>[MALD] There's no point
in coming up with excuses.</b></Default>

6
00:00:21,399 --> 00:00:24,159
<Default><b>All of us saw you break this
with our own two eyes.</b></Default>

7
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,400
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

8
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,960
<Default><b>But I promise I didn't!</b></Default>

9
00:00:28,489 --> 00:00:30,256
<Default><b>[MALD] Your lies mean
nothing to us.</b></Default>

10
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:32,880
<Default><b>[RISHIA] I really don't know
anything about it!</b></Default>

11
00:00:33,079 --> 00:00:34,990
<Default><b>Not even an
apology, huh?</b></Default>

12
00:00:35,579 --> 00:00:36,726
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

13
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:39,590
<Default><b>Then I'm afraid I have
to ask you to leave our party.</b></Default>

14
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:41,920
<Default><b>[gasps] But Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

15
00:00:42,079 --> 00:00:44,396
<Default><b>- I didn't, I'm telling the...
- That's enough, Rishia.</b></Default>

16
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,700
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [ITSUKI] It doesn't matter.</b></Default>

17
00:00:47,210 --> 00:00:49,770
<Default><b>You've been nothing more
than a burden for us.</b></Default>

18
00:00:49,969 --> 00:00:51,129
<Default><b>[swishing]</b></Default>

19
00:00:51,219 --> 00:00:54,140
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

20
00:00:54,350 --> 00:00:56,350
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir
Itsuki, I promise.</b></Default>

21
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:00,649
<Default><b>I promise I'll
become stronger!</b></Default>

22
00:01:02,939 --> 00:01:04,739
<Default><b>And prove I
can be useful!</b></Default>

23
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:08,319
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

24
00:01:09,439 --> 00:01:11,489
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

25
00:01:11,950 --> 00:01:14,550
<Default><b>[ELRASLA] Your ki isn't
focused at all, Rishia.</b></Default>

26
00:01:14,659 --> 00:01:15,700
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

27
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:18,305
<Default><b>[ELRASLA]
Your technique needs work.</b></Default>

28
00:01:18,329 --> 00:01:19,729
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Master!</b></Default>

29
00:01:19,909 --> 00:01:22,269
<Default><b>How about some training
to iron that out?</b></Default>

30
00:01:22,370 --> 00:01:23,459
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

31
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,049
<Default><b>Sure! Thank
you so must...</b></Default>

32
00:01:26,340 --> 00:01:27,340
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

33
00:02:59,099 --> 00:03:00,969
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

34
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:05,270
<Default><b>Now then</b></Default>

35
00:03:05,389 --> 00:03:07,086
<Default><b>This is gonna
hit our budget hard.</b></Default>

36
00:03:07,110 --> 00:03:09,360
<Default><b>- You can say that again.
- Raphy.</b></Default>

37
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,660
<Default><b>- [Gaelion squeaking]
- Hm?</b></Default>

38
00:03:11,819 --> 00:03:14,466
<Default><b>I'm the only one here allowed
to give rides to master.</b></Default>

39
00:03:14,490 --> 00:03:16,819
<Default><b>- [squeaking]
- No, I'm the only one!</b></Default>

40
00:03:18,449 --> 00:03:19,370
<Default><b>That's enough.</b></Default>

41
00:03:19,449 --> 00:03:21,216
<Default><b>It doesn't matter
you can both do it.</b></Default>

42
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,880
<Default><b>It definitely matters!</b></Default>

43
00:03:23,539 --> 00:03:24,750
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

44
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,226
<Default><b>I'm sorry, Gaelion</b></Default>

45
00:03:26,250 --> 00:03:28,186
<Default><b>but you're going to timeout
for a while.</b></Default>

46
00:03:28,210 --> 00:03:30,879
<Default><b>- [squeaking]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

47
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:32,395
<Default><b>What's the big idea?</b></Default>

48
00:03:32,419 --> 00:03:34,026
<Default><b>Don't bully
Gaelion like that!</b></Default>

49
00:03:34,050 --> 00:03:36,180
<Default><b>It's not bullying</b></Default>

50
00:03:36,259 --> 00:03:39,050
<Default><b>Well, he did cause
a lot of trouble for us.</b></Default>

51
00:03:39,139 --> 00:03:40,139
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

52
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,470
<Default><b>Hm. Hm.</b></Default>

53
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:44,060
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] And Filo</b></Default>

54
00:03:44,270 --> 00:03:45,389
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

55
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:46,665
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
We got lucky</b></Default>

56
00:03:46,689 --> 00:03:49,089
<Default><b>'cause whatever happened
broke your curse.</b></Default>

57
00:03:49,729 --> 00:03:50,939
<Default><b>You got it!</b></Default>

58
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:53,545
<Default><b>Hey Melty!
You should come with me</b></Default>

59
00:03:53,569 --> 00:03:55,415
<Default><b>so that we can level up
together!</b></Default>

60
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:57,039
<Default><b>- Huh?
- It'll be fun!</b></Default>

61
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,840
<Default><b>We can get strong
and have Master play with us!</b></Default>

62
00:03:59,949 --> 00:04:01,295
<Default><b>But I can't Filo!</b></Default>

63
00:04:01,319 --> 00:04:02,765
<Default><b>I don't have
time to level!</b></Default>

64
00:04:02,789 --> 00:04:04,346
<Default><b>And there's so
much work to do.</b></Default>

65
00:04:04,370 --> 00:04:06,806
<Default><b>I have to catch up on what
I missed while I was away.</b></Default>

66
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:08,879
<Default><b>What? Come on, Melty.</b></Default>

67
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:11,105
<Default><b>You were just saying
you wanted a higher level!</b></Default>

68
00:04:11,129 --> 00:04:13,026
<Default><b>Well, yeah, but
not right now!</b></Default>

69
00:04:13,050 --> 00:04:15,090
<Default><b>[gasps] Remember, Melty</b></Default>

70
00:04:15,210 --> 00:04:16,605
<Default><b>when you got mad before
and said</b></Default>

71
00:04:16,629 --> 00:04:19,009
<Default><b>"If you can't
do it today</b></Default>

72
00:04:19,089 --> 00:04:20,156
<Default><b>[MELTY] I know but...</b></Default>

73
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:21,526
<Default><b>[FILO] You said that
even if you're busy...</b></Default>

74
00:04:21,550 --> 00:04:22,615
<Default><b>How typical.</b></Default>

75
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:25,639
<Default><b>She's not going to give up
until Melty gives in, is she?</b></Default>

76
00:04:25,769 --> 00:04:27,129
<Default><b>Definitely not.</b></Default>

77
00:04:27,269 --> 00:04:29,165
<Default><b>[MELTY] But I'm telling you
I can't do it Filo!</b></Default>

78
00:04:29,189 --> 00:04:30,389
<Default><b>[FILO] Why?</b></Default>

79
00:04:32,939 --> 00:04:35,179
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Everybody's here now, right?</b></Default>

80
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:38,425
<Default><b>Princess Melty will be gone
for a while.</b></Default>

81
00:04:38,449 --> 00:04:40,045
<Default><b>She left to go
on a journey</b></Default>

82
00:04:40,069 --> 00:04:42,410
<Default><b>to become stronger</b></Default>

83
00:04:42,829 --> 00:04:43,829
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

84
00:04:44,329 --> 00:04:46,000
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

85
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:47,959
<Default><b>Hooray!</b></Default>

86
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:49,976
<Default><b>"Left on a journey?"</b></Default>

87
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,680
<Default><b>I never agreed to this!</b></Default>

88
00:04:51,790 --> 00:04:53,646
<Default><b>That's what we're
telling people.</b></Default>

89
00:04:53,670 --> 00:04:56,430
<Default><b>Make sure everybody in town
knows it. Okay, Éclair?</b></Default>

90
00:04:56,509 --> 00:04:57,855
<Default><b>Y-yes, right away.</b></Default>

91
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,446
<Default><b>Hey, hold on a second!</b></Default>

92
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:00,985
<Default><b>You can't just
decide that!</b></Default>

93
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:03,235
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I got permission
from the Shadows.</b></Default>

94
00:05:03,259 --> 00:05:05,810
<Default><b>Believe it or not</b></Default>

95
00:05:06,019 --> 00:05:06,850
<Default><b>[MELTY] Huh?</b></Default>

96
00:05:06,930 --> 00:05:09,690
<Default><b>Look, you've got plenty
of magical potential, Melty</b></Default>

97
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:11,456
<Default><b>but they've been worried
for a while</b></Default>

98
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,086
<Default><b>that your
level's too low.</b></Default>

99
00:05:13,110 --> 00:05:15,295
<Default><b>For someone running
the country at least.</b></Default>

100
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,836
<Default><b>He's correct,
I dare say.</b></Default>

101
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:18,875
<Default><b>But leaving like this
so suddenly is...</b></Default>

102
00:05:18,899 --> 00:05:20,375
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
All right then, Filo.</b></Default>

103
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:22,675
<Default><b>I'm counting on you
to level up with Melty.</b></Default>

104
00:05:22,699 --> 00:05:24,240
<Default><b>- Wait!
- Hooray!</b></Default>

105
00:05:24,529 --> 00:05:25,846
<Default><b>Are you ready, Melty?</b></Default>

106
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:29,079
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

107
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:30,685
<Default><b>No, I'm not ready!</b></Default>

108
00:05:30,709 --> 00:05:33,540
<Default><b>- And I never said anything...
- Off we go!</b></Default>

109
00:05:33,629 --> 00:05:36,050
<Default><b>-Raphy -Naofumi!</b></Default>

110
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:40,509
<Default><b>[MELTY] I promise
you're gonna regret this!</b></Default>

111
00:05:42,339 --> 00:05:44,059
<Default><b>A leveling journey, huh?</b></Default>

112
00:05:44,389 --> 00:05:45,406
<Default><b>What of it?</b></Default>

113
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:47,310
<Default><b>Princess or not</b></Default>

114
00:05:47,470 --> 00:05:49,696
<Default><b>And kids need to play
every now and then.</b></Default>

115
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:52,576
<Default><b>And with Filo and Raphy
there with her, she'll be safe.</b></Default>

116
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,600
<Default><b>I hope she
manages to have fun.</b></Default>

117
00:05:54,810 --> 00:05:56,730
<Default><b>I'm sure they'll
all be fine.</b></Default>

118
00:05:57,149 --> 00:05:58,939
<Default><b>If you've got work to do</b></Default>

119
00:06:02,569 --> 00:06:03,990
<Default><b>- Eclair.
- Huh.</b></Default>

120
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,795
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
While Melty's gone</b></Default>

121
00:06:05,819 --> 00:06:07,466
<Default><b>I'm going to need you
to act as ruler</b></Default>

122
00:06:07,490 --> 00:06:09,530
<Default><b>and handle her
day-to-day duties.</b></Default>

123
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,226
<Default><b>A-are you
sure about that?</b></Default>

124
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:13,420
<Default><b>I mean, after all</b></Default>

125
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:15,435
<Default><b>Who do you think's
been picking up the work</b></Default>

126
00:06:15,459 --> 00:06:17,016
<Default><b>while you've
been slacking off?</b></Default>

127
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,920
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

128
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,960
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] You've been relying
on Melty too much, Eclair.</b></Default>

129
00:06:21,170 --> 00:06:22,170
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

130
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:25,026
<Default><b>[REN] If there's something
I can do to help.</b></Default>

131
00:06:25,050 --> 00:06:26,050
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

132
00:06:26,259 --> 00:06:27,899
<Default><b>Am I allowed to do so?</b></Default>

133
00:06:28,509 --> 00:06:29,615
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

134
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:31,999
<Default><b>If that's what you
want to do, then sure.</b></Default>

135
00:06:35,149 --> 00:06:36,309
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

136
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,520
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

137
00:06:40,779 --> 00:06:42,059
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

138
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:44,479
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Are you okay, Sadeena?</b></Default>

139
00:06:44,949 --> 00:06:47,199
<Default><b>I'm fine! It's
nothing! [Gasps]</b></Default>

140
00:06:47,779 --> 00:06:48,819
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

141
00:06:50,370 --> 00:06:52,090
<Default><b>Is something the matter?</b></Default>

142
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:54,055
<Default><b>Do you have to show up
out of nowhere?</b></Default>

143
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,266
<Default><b>[S'yne's
stomach growling]</b></Default>

144
00:06:55,290 --> 00:06:57,185
<Default><b>[chuckles] Guess that means
it's time to eat.</b></Default>

145
00:06:57,209 --> 00:06:58,329
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

146
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:00,250
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

147
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,220
<Default><b>[S'YNE]
Thank you kindly.</b></Default>

148
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:04,855
<Default><b>[DOLL]
It was delicious!</b></Default>

149
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:07,009
<Default><b>So then</b></Default>

150
00:07:07,389 --> 00:07:10,069
<Default><b>We sure had a hell of a time
while you were gone.</b></Default>

151
00:07:10,139 --> 00:07:11,406
<Default><b>Well, if I'm
not mistaken</b></Default>

152
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:13,865
<Default><b>S'yne was busy doing
some work underground.</b></Default>

153
00:07:13,889 --> 00:07:14,889
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

154
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:16,456
<Default><b>Underground?</b></Default>

155
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,480
<Default><b>She means
the underground arena.</b></Default>

156
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:20,480
<Default><b>[DOLL] And of course</b></Default>

157
00:07:20,569 --> 00:07:23,129
<Default><b>half of what I earned
down there, Sir Naofumi!</b></Default>

158
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:24,839
<Default><b>[coins clinking]</b></Default>

159
00:07:25,149 --> 00:07:27,160
<Default><b>Nice! Keep the
money coming!</b></Default>

160
00:07:27,410 --> 00:07:29,490
<Default><b>That's not very nice</b></Default>

161
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,596
<Default><b>Just what I expect
from Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

162
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:33,346
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Why would you
expect that from him?</b></Default>

163
00:07:33,370 --> 00:07:35,850
<Default><b>I'm impressed you managed
to make this much!</b></Default>

164
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:38,146
<Default><b>And in such a short period
of time too!</b></Default>

165
00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:40,170
<Default><b>Somebody made
even more than me.</b></Default>

166
00:07:40,589 --> 00:07:42,226
<Default><b>[DOLL]
There's a rumor going around</b></Default>

167
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:44,026
<Default><b>about an archer
who's been seen fighting</b></Default>

168
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:46,050
<Default><b>at a different
arena every day.</b></Default>

169
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:48,550
<Default><b>An archer? Could it be?</b></Default>

170
00:07:49,589 --> 00:07:51,350
<Default><b>Hm. From what I heard</b></Default>

171
00:07:52,009 --> 00:07:54,245
<Default><b>their name is
"Perfect Hidden Justice."</b></Default>

172
00:07:54,269 --> 00:07:55,469
<Default><b>[all gasps]</b></Default>

173
00:07:55,889 --> 00:07:57,609
<Default><b>Hold on, there's no way.</b></Default>

174
00:07:57,730 --> 00:08:00,010
<Default><b>I mean with a ridiculous name
like that</b></Default>

175
00:08:00,189 --> 00:08:02,149
<Default><b>who else could
it possibly be?</b></Default>

176
00:08:04,149 --> 00:08:06,819
<Default><b>Who you're talking about</b></Default>

177
00:08:07,740 --> 00:08:10,529
<Default><b>While it's possible</b></Default>

178
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:12,555
<Default><b>But it's worth
us checking out.</b></Default>

179
00:08:12,579 --> 00:08:14,346
<Default><b>You're going
back to the arena?</b></Default>

180
00:08:14,370 --> 00:08:15,726
<Default><b>Then I want
to go this time!</b></Default>

181
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:17,305
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
We're not going to goof off.</b></Default>

182
00:08:17,329 --> 00:08:18,516
<Default><b>I know that!</b></Default>

183
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:20,750
<Default><b>Come on!
It'll help me get stronger!</b></Default>

184
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:22,420
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

185
00:08:22,459 --> 00:08:24,185
<Default><b>[ELRASLA] You know you really
should take her with you.</b></Default>

186
00:08:24,209 --> 00:08:25,879
<Default><b>- Hm.
- She'd do well</b></Default>

187
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,406
<Default><b>fighting mercenaries.</b></Default>

188
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:29,276
<Default><b>As opposed to fighting
the same people</b></Default>

189
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:31,156
<Default><b>all the time here
in the village.</b></Default>

190
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,180
<Default><b>Aah!</b></Default>

191
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,115
<Default><b>[ELRASLA]
I can confidently say</b></Default>

192
00:08:35,139 --> 00:08:37,819
<Default><b>she's more than strong enough
now to fight there.</b></Default>

193
00:08:38,769 --> 00:08:41,110
<Default><b>- [swords clanging]
- [both grunt]</b></Default>

194
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:46,190
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

195
00:08:48,450 --> 00:08:50,529
<Default><b>[KEEL]
Wow! This is awesome!</b></Default>

196
00:08:51,370 --> 00:08:53,635
<Default><b>Are we really gonna get
to fight in here?</b></Default>

197
00:08:53,659 --> 00:08:56,346
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yeah. Just don't do
anything dumb, okay?</b></Default>

198
00:08:56,370 --> 00:08:58,210
<Default><b>[KEEL]
All right, all right!</b></Default>

199
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:00,750
<Default><b>Fohl decided
not to come with us?</b></Default>

200
00:09:01,169 --> 00:09:03,289
<Default><b>I think he realized
how weak he was</b></Default>

201
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:05,860
<Default><b>and stayed behind
with the old lady to train.</b></Default>

202
00:09:06,549 --> 00:09:09,025
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] The two of them
were both really fired up.</b></Default>

203
00:09:09,049 --> 00:09:11,769
<Default><b>So I can't imagine how hard
she's gonna be on him.</b></Default>

204
00:09:13,139 --> 00:09:14,939
<Default><b>- [audience cheering]
- Hm.</b></Default>

205
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:17,535
<Default><b>[SALVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
How good to see you.</b></Default>

206
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:19,319
<Default><b>Welcome back
Shield Hero!</b></Default>

207
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:22,666
<Default><b>I take it the little ones
before you here</b></Default>

208
00:09:22,690 --> 00:09:24,456
<Default><b>are today's
entrants, yes?</b></Default>

209
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,416
<Default><b>They look exactly
how I pictured slaves</b></Default>

210
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,440
<Default><b>of the Shield Hero
to look like!</b></Default>

211
00:09:28,529 --> 00:09:30,625
<Default><b>After all, each one of them
has a fire</b></Default>

212
00:09:30,649 --> 00:09:32,950
<Default><b>- burning in their eyes!
- [ALL] Hmm.</b></Default>

213
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,926
<Default><b>Oh, not to worry!</b></Default>

214
00:09:34,950 --> 00:09:37,135
<Default><b>I can safely assure you
that today's tournament</b></Default>

215
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:39,159
<Default><b>is more for sport
than anything.</b></Default>

216
00:09:39,289 --> 00:09:41,409
<Default><b>I promise
there's no need to worry!</b></Default>

217
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:43,830
<Default><b>Sadeena, you're
in charge here.</b></Default>

218
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,186
<Default><b>Sure thing.</b></Default>

219
00:09:45,210 --> 00:09:47,105
<Default><b>I promise
everything will be fine!</b></Default>

220
00:09:47,129 --> 00:09:48,936
<Default><b>Listen up, make sure
you're careful</b></Default>

221
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,235
<Default><b>when you're fighting
down there.</b></Default>

222
00:09:50,259 --> 00:09:51,459
<Default><b>[ALL] Okay.</b></Default>

223
00:09:52,009 --> 00:09:54,389
<Default><b>All right! Let's
get going!</b></Default>

224
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:57,220
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN BOY 10-A]
All right.</b></Default>

225
00:09:58,429 --> 00:09:59,456
<Default><b>Now then.</b></Default>

226
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:02,035
<Default><b>I've been told you have
a question for me Shield Hero.</b></Default>

227
00:10:02,059 --> 00:10:04,706
<Default><b>Yes. Do you know if one
of the contestants here today</b></Default>

228
00:10:04,730 --> 00:10:07,130
<Default><b>is an archer named
Perfect Hidden Justice?</b></Default>

229
00:10:09,029 --> 00:10:10,029
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

230
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:14,909
<Default><b>[gasps] Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

231
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:17,990
<Default><b>- Huh. Wait, Rishia!
- Where did she go?</b></Default>

232
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:21,370
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

233
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:22,936
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

234
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:29,960
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

235
00:10:30,629 --> 00:10:32,759
<Default><b>Wait. Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

236
00:10:36,549 --> 00:10:39,559
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

237
00:10:39,929 --> 00:10:41,489
<Default><b>What was that about?</b></Default>

238
00:10:41,929 --> 00:10:43,449
<Default><b>- Sir Itsuki!
- Huh?</b></Default>

239
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:45,159
<Default><b>[REN] Hey, isn't that.</b></Default>

240
00:10:46,730 --> 00:10:48,170
<Default><b>It really is him.</b></Default>

241
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,359
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

242
00:10:52,990 --> 00:10:54,550
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

243
00:10:54,950 --> 00:10:56,296
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
My oh my.</b></Default>

244
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,755
<Default><b>You all started running
so quickly</b></Default>

245
00:10:57,779 --> 00:11:00,019
<Default><b>I thought I'd never
catch up with you!</b></Default>

246
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:02,726
<Default><b>Is that man with the bow
the one you're looking for?</b></Default>

247
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:05,159
<Default><b>Since the match
hasn't started</b></Default>

248
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:07,379
<Default><b>Yes. I suppose
just for you</b></Default>

249
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:09,855
<Default><b>I could bend the rules
and make a small exception!</b></Default>

250
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:10,960
<Default><b>Go on!</b></Default>

251
00:11:11,629 --> 00:11:13,049
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

252
00:11:13,259 --> 00:11:19,389
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

253
00:11:21,269 --> 00:11:22,829
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

254
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:26,649
<Default><b>Its, uh, been a while</b></Default>

255
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:28,836
<Default><b>- You see, I've...
- [ITSUKI] Everything's fine.</b></Default>

256
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:30,610
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] I... Yes.</b></Default>

257
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,760
<Default><b>Everyone is...</b></Default>

258
00:11:32,899 --> 00:11:34,419
<Default><b>Is everything okay?</b></Default>

259
00:11:34,570 --> 00:11:36,010
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Hm. Yes.</b></Default>

260
00:11:36,740 --> 00:11:38,860
<Default><b>Everyone wants
the Bow Hero's help.</b></Default>

261
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:41,385
<Default><b>And the prize money
I win today</b></Default>

262
00:11:41,409 --> 00:11:43,249
<Default><b>- will save lives.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

263
00:11:43,330 --> 00:11:45,539
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki!
What's going on?</b></Default>

264
00:11:45,789 --> 00:11:47,145
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] That's right.</b></Default>

265
00:11:47,169 --> 00:11:49,289
<Default><b>I'm just as strong
as I used to be.</b></Default>

266
00:11:49,669 --> 00:11:52,629
<Default><b>I'm a servant
of justice!</b></Default>

267
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,040
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

268
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,816
<Default><b>[both grunt]</b></Default>

269
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,320
<Default><b>- Rishia!
- Rishia!</b></Default>

270
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:02,400
<Default><b>- [RAPHTALIA] Are you okay?
- [Rishia whimpering]</b></Default>

271
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,840
<Default><b>Hey, Itsuki.</b></Default>

272
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:08,559
<Default><b>So, Naofumi.</b></Default>

273
00:12:10,019 --> 00:12:12,419
<Default><b>- [ITSUKI] She told me you know.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

274
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,690
<Default><b>Princess Malty
told me everything</b></Default>

275
00:12:15,029 --> 00:12:16,709
<Default><b>about what you've done!</b></Default>

276
00:12:16,899 --> 00:12:17,939
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

277
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:19,966
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Why the hell
am I hearing Witch's name</b></Default>

278
00:12:19,990 --> 00:12:21,046
<Default><b>from your lips?</b></Default>

279
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:22,390
<Default><b>Don't tell me.</b></Default>

280
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:24,790
<Default><b>She's traveling
with you now?</b></Default>

281
00:12:24,830 --> 00:12:26,635
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
And so what if she is?</b></Default>

282
00:12:26,659 --> 00:12:29,099
<Default><b>Who's in my party
is none of your business.</b></Default>

283
00:12:29,169 --> 00:12:31,960
<Default><b>Trust me, Itsuki</b></Default>

284
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:34,970
<Default><b>[REN] ] Do what he says.
Nothing she says is true.</b></Default>

285
00:12:35,090 --> 00:12:37,090
<Default><b>She's feeding
you lies, Itsuki.</b></Default>

286
00:12:37,509 --> 00:12:39,025
<Default><b>How can you
even say that</b></Default>

287
00:12:39,049 --> 00:12:40,735
<Default><b>when you don't know
what it is she said?</b></Default>

288
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,279
<Default><b>Because I know her!</b></Default>

289
00:12:42,970 --> 00:12:44,730
<Default><b>[REN]
I know her too well.</b></Default>

290
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:46,285
<Default><b>"Whatever you're doing
is right.</b></Default>

291
00:12:46,309 --> 00:12:48,365
<Default><b>I'm the only one
who believes you!"</b></Default>

292
00:12:48,389 --> 00:12:51,109
<Default><b>She's saying exactly
what you want to hear, right?</b></Default>

293
00:12:51,649 --> 00:12:53,089
<Default><b>They're all lies!</b></Default>

294
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:55,610
<Default><b>To manipulate you
the way she did with us!</b></Default>

295
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:56,940
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

296
00:12:59,149 --> 00:13:01,029
<Default><b>I'm clearly
wasting my time.</b></Default>

297
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:03,966
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
My round is about to begin.</b></Default>

298
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:05,539
<Default><b>Huh. Itsuki wait!</b></Default>

299
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,200
<Default><b>Itsuki.</b></Default>

300
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,160
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

301
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:16,436
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Ah, participant number 982.</b></Default>

302
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:17,775
<Default><b>If I recall correctly</b></Default>

303
00:13:17,799 --> 00:13:19,759
<Default><b>that's Perfect
Hidden Justice</b></Default>

304
00:13:20,129 --> 00:13:21,696
<Default><b>I believe if I'm
not mistaken</b></Default>

305
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:24,275
<Default><b>it was right after you left
the arena last time</b></Default>

306
00:13:24,299 --> 00:13:27,559
<Default><b>that I first saw him enter
my arena as a participant.</b></Default>

307
00:13:28,519 --> 00:13:31,245
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It's just like
the rumors S'yne heard, then.</b></Default>

308
00:13:31,269 --> 00:13:32,269
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

309
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:35,269
<Default><b>Naofumi, I'm glad
we found him, but what now?</b></Default>

310
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,920
<Default><b>From the look of it.</b></Default>

311
00:13:37,029 --> 00:13:39,240
<Default><b>Yeah. We're not gonna
be able to have</b></Default>

312
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:41,120
<Default><b>a productive
conversation.</b></Default>

313
00:13:41,409 --> 00:13:42,449
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

314
00:13:43,409 --> 00:13:45,926
<Default><b>What if we knock him
unconscious and capture him?</b></Default>

315
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:47,596
<Default><b>That would
work, wouldn't it?</b></Default>

316
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:50,120
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Or simply speak to him</b></Default>

317
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,476
<Default><b>using our fists.</b></Default>

318
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:54,129
<Default><b>Why are both of those choices
equally violent?</b></Default>

319
00:13:54,419 --> 00:13:55,936
<Default><b>- [RAPHTALIA] Goodness.
- I'd rather work</b></Default>

320
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,880
<Default><b>things out
peacefully, but...</b></Default>

321
00:13:58,169 --> 00:13:59,855
<Default><b>If Bitch
is travelling with him</b></Default>

322
00:13:59,879 --> 00:14:01,235
<Default><b>then there's
not much time.</b></Default>

323
00:14:01,259 --> 00:14:03,009
<Default><b>Yeah. And also</b></Default>

324
00:14:03,090 --> 00:14:05,450
<Default><b>there's those enemies
S'yne talked about.</b></Default>

325
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:07,959
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] What do we do?
- [gasps]</b></Default>

326
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:12,769
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

327
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,660
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] They're wrong.</b></Default>

328
00:14:14,769 --> 00:14:16,690
<Default><b>I'm not being
lied to here.</b></Default>

329
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,960
<Default><b>I'm not in the wrong.</b></Default>

330
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:24,135
<Default><b>I'll never forget
all the looks of disgust</b></Default>

331
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:25,999
<Default><b>I've gotten
since that day.</b></Default>

332
00:14:27,490 --> 00:14:29,410
<Default><b>The words
they've said to me.</b></Default>

333
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:32,720
<Default><b>That's right.
They're the ones in the wrong!</b></Default>

334
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,120
<Default><b>Not me!</b></Default>

335
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:37,186
<Default><b>And that's what
Princess Malty said</b></Default>

336
00:14:37,210 --> 00:14:38,730
<Default><b>so it must be true.</b></Default>

337
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,129
<Default><b>Although we parted ways
once before</b></Default>

338
00:14:42,379 --> 00:14:44,775
<Default><b>Mald and the others
came back to me again.</b></Default>

339
00:14:44,799 --> 00:14:47,259
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

340
00:14:47,429 --> 00:14:48,826
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] That's right.</b></Default>

341
00:14:48,850 --> 00:14:50,930
<Default><b>Everybody wants me
in their party.</b></Default>

342
00:14:51,019 --> 00:14:52,539
<Default><b>That's why I fight.</b></Default>

343
00:14:53,179 --> 00:14:54,916
<Default><b>So for the sake
of Princess Malty</b></Default>

344
00:14:54,940 --> 00:14:56,980
<Default><b>and my comrades
who believe in me</b></Default>

345
00:14:57,769 --> 00:14:59,505
<Default><b>I'll continue
pushing forward!</b></Default>

346
00:14:59,529 --> 00:15:02,529
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

347
00:15:03,450 --> 00:15:06,450
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

348
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:09,100
<Default><b>[spear swishing]</b></Default>

349
00:15:09,950 --> 00:15:12,159
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

350
00:15:12,539 --> 00:15:15,539
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

351
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:17,936
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I knew it.</b></Default>

352
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,640
<Default><b>He hasn't powered up
his Cardinal Weapon, either.</b></Default>

353
00:15:21,169 --> 00:15:22,889
<Default><b>And that bow he's using.</b></Default>

354
00:15:23,669 --> 00:15:25,989
<Default><b>I don't like the feeling
it's giving me!</b></Default>

355
00:15:26,179 --> 00:15:27,235
<Default><b>- [blood splatters]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

356
00:15:27,259 --> 00:15:28,299
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

357
00:15:28,470 --> 00:15:30,970
<Default><b>Rishia, are you're okay
watching this?</b></Default>

358
00:15:31,259 --> 00:15:32,859
<Default><b>Mm-hmm. I'll be okay.</b></Default>

359
00:15:32,929 --> 00:15:34,615
<Default><b>Though it is a little...</b></Default>

360
00:15:34,639 --> 00:15:35,679
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

361
00:15:35,809 --> 00:15:38,559
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

362
00:15:38,690 --> 00:15:40,480
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

363
00:15:40,730 --> 00:15:43,740
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

364
00:15:44,610 --> 00:15:47,490
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

365
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:51,200
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

366
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,800
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]</b></Default>

367
00:16:02,379 --> 00:16:03,619
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

368
00:16:05,419 --> 00:16:06,779
<Default><b>[Rishia grunts]</b></Default>

369
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:08,775
<Default><b>I beg of you!</b></Default>

370
00:16:08,799 --> 00:16:11,039
<Default><b>Let me be the one
to fight Sir Itsuki!</b></Default>

371
00:16:11,850 --> 00:16:13,326
<Default><b>Please, Sir Naofumi?</b></Default>

372
00:16:13,350 --> 00:16:14,990
<Default><b>You want to fight him?</b></Default>

373
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:17,510
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Yes!
I want to talk to him.</b></Default>

374
00:16:17,690 --> 00:16:20,059
<Default><b>You see, I've always wanted
to repay him</b></Default>

375
00:16:20,149 --> 00:16:21,245
<Default><b>for saving my life</b></Default>

376
00:16:21,269 --> 00:16:23,629
<Default><b>but I just haven't
had the chance to yet.</b></Default>

377
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:27,176
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Back when
we were in the same party</b></Default>

378
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,320
<Default><b>I was completely
useless to him.</b></Default>

379
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:32,046
<Default><b>I wasn't allowed
to fight with them</b></Default>

380
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:34,120
<Default><b>so I just did
menial jobs.</b></Default>

381
00:16:35,159 --> 00:16:36,639
<Default><b>Because I was weak</b></Default>

382
00:16:36,789 --> 00:16:38,919
<Default><b>I was nothing
but a burden to him.</b></Default>

383
00:16:39,879 --> 00:16:41,210
<Default><b>I had no idea.</b></Default>

384
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:44,710
<Default><b>To be fair though, my stats
were actually really low.</b></Default>

385
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:48,446
<Default><b>But in the time that
I've spent alongside you</b></Default>

386
00:16:48,470 --> 00:16:50,155
<Default><b>I've seen you
and your comrades</b></Default>

387
00:16:50,179 --> 00:16:52,179
<Default><b>save each other
again and again!</b></Default>

388
00:16:52,889 --> 00:16:54,089
<Default><b>And so now.</b></Default>

389
00:16:56,139 --> 00:16:57,365
<Default><b>Unlike before</b></Default>

390
00:16:57,389 --> 00:16:59,326
<Default><b>when I see him
suffering like this</b></Default>

391
00:16:59,350 --> 00:17:01,070
<Default><b>I feel I can help, so...</b></Default>

392
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:04,360
<Default><b>Look, I understand
how you feel.</b></Default>

393
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,505
<Default><b>But he's not going to listen
to reason right now.</b></Default>

394
00:17:06,529 --> 00:17:08,849
<Default><b>[Rishia] That's why
I want to fight him!</b></Default>

395
00:17:08,950 --> 00:17:11,279
<Default><b>If it's a fight</b></Default>

396
00:17:14,869 --> 00:17:16,676
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Pardon me, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

397
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:18,426
<Default><b>But I think I might have
just the thing</b></Default>

398
00:17:18,450 --> 00:17:19,936
<Default><b>to help you
in your fight.</b></Default>

399
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:20,960
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

400
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:24,710
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

401
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:28,696
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Here's the money I made today.</b></Default>

402
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:31,240
<Default><b>[MALD] Nicely done.
Even more than last time!</b></Default>

403
00:17:31,380 --> 00:17:33,196
<Default><b>[SPEARWOMAN]
Right? I'm so impressed!</b></Default>

404
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:35,420
<Default><b>Thank you for doing
all this, Itsuki.</b></Default>

405
00:17:35,509 --> 00:17:37,099
<Default><b>- Hm.
- Hm?</b></Default>

406
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:39,150
<Default><b>What, is
something wrong?</b></Default>

407
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:42,559
<Default><b>No. It's just
we still don't have enough.</b></Default>

408
00:17:42,849 --> 00:17:44,745
<Default><b>Not if we want to rescue
the slaves.</b></Default>

409
00:17:44,769 --> 00:17:46,876
<Default><b>And when I think of the kids
we can't save...</b></Default>

410
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:48,456
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
Don't you worry about that.</b></Default>

411
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,360
<Default><b>Just leave
everything to me.</b></Default>

412
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:51,480
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

413
00:17:51,529 --> 00:17:53,595
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] As long as
I have you by my side</b></Default>

414
00:17:53,619 --> 00:17:55,345
<Default><b>along with this bow
you gave me</b></Default>

415
00:17:55,369 --> 00:17:56,740
<Default><b>I'm sure. No.</b></Default>

416
00:17:57,369 --> 00:17:59,710
<Default><b>I swear. I'll
save all of them!</b></Default>

417
00:18:00,289 --> 00:18:01,579
<Default><b>Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

418
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:04,670
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Oh, and I ran
into Naofumi there.</b></Default>

419
00:18:04,839 --> 00:18:06,130
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

420
00:18:06,750 --> 00:18:08,646
<Default><b>[ITSUKI]
It's exactly as you said.</b></Default>

421
00:18:08,670 --> 00:18:10,590
<Default><b>He has slaves
there with him.</b></Default>

422
00:18:10,630 --> 00:18:13,640
<Default><b>And... he said
I was being lied to.</b></Default>

423
00:18:15,470 --> 00:18:17,995
<Default><b>[MALD] D-do you think
that we're lying to you?</b></Default>

424
00:18:18,019 --> 00:18:20,179
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] Of course not.
Why would I?</b></Default>

425
00:18:20,730 --> 00:18:22,390
<Default><b>But don't worry</b></Default>

426
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:24,400
<Default><b>will come around
in due time.</b></Default>

427
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:27,360
<Default><b>I'll make enough prize money
to free all of the slaves.</b></Default>

428
00:18:28,109 --> 00:18:30,469
<Default><b>And show him
we're the ones in the right.</b></Default>

429
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:31,990
<Default><b>Good.</b></Default>

430
00:18:34,819 --> 00:18:36,545
<Default><b>[HOODED MAN 10-A]
The Shield Hero's here?</b></Default>

431
00:18:36,569 --> 00:18:37,966
<Default><b>[MYNE]
Sorry to disappoint</b></Default>

432
00:18:37,990 --> 00:18:41,095
<Default><b>but we won't be able to sell
the boy into slavery after all.</b></Default>

433
00:18:41,119 --> 00:18:42,136
<Default><b>[HOODED MAN 10-A] Yes.</b></Default>

434
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,976
<Default><b>He's young enough
to be worth a lot</b></Default>

435
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,265
<Default><b>but he's already made us
a lot of money.</b></Default>

436
00:18:46,289 --> 00:18:47,356
<Default><b>We've made enough.</b></Default>

437
00:18:47,380 --> 00:18:48,936
<Default><b>[MYNE] I don't think so.</b></Default>

438
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:50,146
<Default><b>I had to put
up with listening</b></Default>

439
00:18:50,170 --> 00:18:52,025
<Default><b>to his childish ideas
of justice</b></Default>

440
00:18:52,049 --> 00:18:54,809
<Default><b>so I'm going to squeeze
every last drop out of him.</b></Default>

441
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,390
<Default><b>I mean</b></Default>

442
00:18:57,680 --> 00:19:00,200
<Default><b>it's my job to teach him
how the world works.</b></Default>

443
00:19:02,930 --> 00:19:04,559
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

444
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:07,019
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

445
00:19:08,650 --> 00:19:10,940
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

446
00:19:11,190 --> 00:19:14,200
<Default><b>[Itsuki screams]</b></Default>

447
00:19:14,910 --> 00:19:16,216
<Default><b>[coins clinking]</b></Default>

448
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,886
<Default><b>[MAN 10-A]
Here's your prize money.</b></Default>

449
00:19:17,910 --> 00:19:19,030
<Default><b>And also.</b></Default>

450
00:19:20,490 --> 00:19:22,055
<Default><b>[ITSUKI] What's this?</b></Default>

451
00:19:22,079 --> 00:19:23,595
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
While he's in the arena</b></Default>

452
00:19:23,619 --> 00:19:24,936
<Default><b>I'm going to have
one of my men</b></Default>

453
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:27,130
<Default><b>send an invitation
to the Bow Hero.</b></Default>

454
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:28,750
<Default><b>And then tonight</b></Default>

455
00:19:28,839 --> 00:19:31,679
<Default><b>I'm going to lure him
into a secret underground arena</b></Default>

456
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:34,196
<Default><b>where the ritual
magic sanctuary has been cast</b></Default>

457
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:36,220
<Default><b>in preparation
for his arrival.</b></Default>

458
00:19:36,930 --> 00:19:38,156
<Default><b>Once it falls into place</b></Default>

459
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:40,275
<Default><b>we will have captured
the Bow Hero!</b></Default>

460
00:19:40,299 --> 00:19:41,899
<Default><b>- Yes!
- [NAOFUMI] Hm.</b></Default>

461
00:19:42,309 --> 00:19:44,916
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Oh? Is there a problem?</b></Default>

462
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:47,380
<Default><b>I wanna know what you gain
from doing this.</b></Default>

463
00:19:47,599 --> 00:19:48,916
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'm sure if you
were to help us</b></Default>

464
00:19:48,940 --> 00:19:50,335
<Default><b>capture the Bow Hero</b></Default>

465
00:19:50,359 --> 00:19:51,626
<Default><b>that the Queen
of Melromarc</b></Default>

466
00:19:51,650 --> 00:19:54,250
<Default><b>would be willing to pay
a healthy reward but...</b></Default>

467
00:19:54,359 --> 00:19:56,650
<Default><b>Just as I'd expect
of the Shield Hero!</b></Default>

468
00:19:56,819 --> 00:19:59,216
<Default><b>I truly am in awe
of your unshakeable ability</b></Default>

469
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:01,829
<Default><b>to sniff out my intentions!
Yes!</b></Default>

470
00:20:01,990 --> 00:20:04,055
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
So what else are you after?</b></Default>

471
00:20:04,079 --> 00:20:05,476
<Default><b>You're not
trying to profit off</b></Default>

472
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:07,146
<Default><b>selling tickets
to the match</b></Default>

473
00:20:07,170 --> 00:20:08,500
<Default><b>But of course.</b></Default>

474
00:20:08,579 --> 00:20:10,686
<Default><b>I just haven't invited
the audience yet!</b></Default>

475
00:20:10,710 --> 00:20:12,270
<Default><b>- Huh?
- [whispering]</b></Default>

476
00:20:13,759 --> 00:20:15,025
<Default><b>I've just been informed</b></Default>

477
00:20:15,049 --> 00:20:17,129
<Default><b>that the Bow Hero
has now arrived.</b></Default>

478
00:20:17,430 --> 00:20:18,299
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

479
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:20,275
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] He's not as strong
as he could be</b></Default>

480
00:20:20,299 --> 00:20:23,099
<Default><b>but it's possible he's affected
by the Curse series.</b></Default>

481
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:24,220
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

482
00:20:24,599 --> 00:20:27,640
<Default><b>Don't worry.
We'll be there the entire time.</b></Default>

483
00:20:28,019 --> 00:20:30,440
<Default><b>If things go bad</b></Default>

484
00:20:31,019 --> 00:20:32,339
<Default><b>[Keel giggles]</b></Default>

485
00:20:34,990 --> 00:20:36,110
<Default><b>Everyone.</b></Default>

486
00:20:36,740 --> 00:20:39,950
<Default><b>Now then, go show Itsuki
the woman you've become!</b></Default>

487
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:42,480
<Default><b>Let him see just
how strong you are now.</b></Default>

488
00:20:43,579 --> 00:20:44,699
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

489
00:20:44,829 --> 00:20:46,660
<Default><b>Okay! I'll do
my blesh...</b></Default>

490
00:20:47,289 --> 00:20:48,289
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

491
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,896
<Default><b>[chains rattling]</b></Default>

492
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,320
<Default><b>[gates rumbling]</b></Default>

493
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:59,380
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

494
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:04,360
<Default><b>The Bow Hero really is
someone important to her.</b></Default>

495
00:21:04,509 --> 00:21:06,909
<Default><b>She's willing to fight him
for their bond.</b></Default>

496
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,519
<Default><b>Without any further ado.</b></Default>

497
00:21:10,769 --> 00:21:13,980
<Default><b>We'll now begin our match
between Rishia Ivyred...</b></Default>

498
00:21:15,650 --> 00:21:19,029
<Default><b>And her opponent</b></Default>

499
00:21:19,450 --> 00:21:22,450
<Default><b>Let the battle
between them begin!</b></Default>

500
00:21:22,529 --> 00:21:24,119
<Default><b>[gong dings]</b></Default>

501
00:21:25,410 --> 00:21:28,410
<Default><b>[audience cheering]</b></Default>

502
00:21:29,250 --> 00:21:31,345
<Default><b>- I haven't done anything yet.
- [RISHIA] Sir Itsuki.</b></Default>

503
00:21:31,369 --> 00:21:32,369
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

504
00:21:35,049 --> 00:21:36,130
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

505
00:21:36,339 --> 00:21:38,419
<Default><b>Are you my opponent
today, Rishia?</b></Default>

506
00:21:39,220 --> 00:21:40,980
<Default><b>If so, this
will be easy.</b></Default>

507
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:43,065
<Default><b>[RISHIA] You saved me
from a despair</b></Default>

508
00:21:43,089 --> 00:21:45,009
<Default><b>I'm unable to
put into words.</b></Default>

509
00:21:45,259 --> 00:21:48,139
<Default><b>[Itsuki sneers] Is that
what you came here to tell me?</b></Default>

510
00:21:49,390 --> 00:21:50,745
<Default><b>And so this time.</b></Default>

511
00:21:50,769 --> 00:21:52,599
<Default><b>- [sword clangs]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

512
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:55,609
<Default><b>It's my turn to save you</b></Default>

513
00:21:55,769 --> 00:22:02,779
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

